&lt;h3 id="registers">Registers&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://light.ryankert.cc/p/risc-v-tips-and-tricks/Screenshot%202024-03-27%20at%2011.39.36%E2%80%AFPM.png"
